Package: gravity
Type: Package
Title: Gravity model with large scale data
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Lino Galiana
Maintainer: Lino Galiana <lino.galiana@insee.fr>
Description: An \code{R} package proposing a series of models related
            to gravity model.
Details: This package is suited for large scale data that fit into memory.
            It is based on \code{Rcpp} and \code{fastglm} to be faster
            and more memory-parcimonious
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: fastglm,
    MASS,
    pscl,
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.2),
    RcppEigen (>= 0.3.3.5.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
References: <Silva, J. S., & Tenreyro, S. (2006). The log of gravity. The Review of Economics and statistics, 88(4), 641-658.>
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    profvis,
    data.table,
    microbenchmark,
    stargazer
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
